Langkah - langkah pembuatan file installer MacOS

1. hdiutil create -fs HFS+ -volname "MyFlutterApp" -srcfolder "build/macos/Build/Products/Release/My Flutter App.app" "MyFlutterAppInstaller.dmg"
2. hdiutil attach "MyFlutterAppInstaller.dmg"
3. sudo bless --folder /Volumes/MyFlutterApp --openfolder /Volumes/MyFlutterApp/Applications
4. hdiutil detach /Volumes/MyFlutterApp

Langkah - langkah pembuatan file installer Windows

1. Download dan intall Inno
2. Buat file script installer
`
; Script generated by the Inno Setup Script Wizard.
; SEE THE DOCUMENTATION FOR DETAILS ON CREATING INNO SETUP SCRIPT FILES!

[Setup]
AppName=MyFlutterApp
AppVersion=1.0
DefaultDirName={pf}\MyFlutterApp
DefaultGroupName=MyFlutterApp
OutputDir=userdocs:Inno Setup Examples Output
OutputBaseFilename=MyFlutterAppInstaller
Compression=lzma
SolidCompression=yes

[Files]
Source: "path\to\MyFlutterApp\*"; DestDir: "{app}"; Flags: ignoreversion recursesubdirs createallsubdirs
`
3. Buka Inno dan lakukan kompilasi.